OL,3,CFirefighters urged to take part in
OL,4,Csurvey around mental health and work
OL,6,FFirefighters have been urged to take
OL,7,Fpart in a study into their mental
OL,8,Fhealth and how it impacts their work.
OL,10,FThe Fire Brigades Union says despite
OL,11,Fthe demanding nature of the role,
OL,12,Fthere is no standardised guidance or
OL,13,Fmental health support specific to
OL,14,Ffirefighters in the UK.
OL,16,FIt has now has commissioned the
OL,17,FUniversity of Central Lancashire to
OL,18,Fcarry out the research to ensure "all
OL,19,Fserving firefighters have their voices
OL,20,Fheard".
