OL,3,CFirefighters urged to take part in
OL,4,Csurvey around mental health and work
OL,6,FIt is hoped a total of 10,000
OL,7,Ffirefighters will be surveyed in the
OL,8,Fstudy which is being led by Dr
OL,9,FCarolina Campodonico, whose area of
OL,10,Fexpertise is trauma, psychosis and
OL,11,Fpost-traumatic growth.
OL,13,FDr Campodonico said: "Firefighters
OL,14,Facross the UK face immense physical
OL,15,Fand emotional demands, yet mental
OL,16,Fhealth support remains inconsistent
OL,17,Fand underutilised.
