OL,3,CFirefighters urged to take part in
OL,4,Csurvey around mental health and work
OL,6,F"This is a vital opportunity for all
OL,7,Fserving firefighters to have their
OL,8,Fvoices heard while remaining
OL,9,Fanonymous."
OL,11,FSimilar surveys have been carried in
OL,12,Fcountries like the US, Canada, and
OL,13,FAustralia, which Dr Campodonico says
OL,14,Fhave "delivered real change", where
OL,15,Fnational policies have "strengthened
OL,16,Fsupport" for first responders.
OL,18,FDr Campodonico continued: "We need to
OL,19,Fensure UK firefighters receive the
OL,20,Fsame level of commitment to their
OL,21,Fmental well-being.
