OL,3,CFirefighters urged to take part in
OL,4,Csurvey around mental health and work
OL,6,F"Our research is independent, shaped
OL,7,Fby the needs of the fire service
OL,8,Fcommunity, and aims to provide clear,
OL,9,Fevidence-based recommendations to
OL,10,Fimprove mental health support.
OL,12,F"Every firefighter who takes part will
OL,13,Fbe helping to create meaningful change
OL,14,F` now is the time to speak up."
OL,16,FFBU general secretary, Steve Wright,
OL,17,Fsaid: "We're calling on all serving
OL,18,Ffirefighters in the UK to take part in
OL,19,Fthis ground-breaking research into
OL,20,Ffirefighter mental health.
