OL,3,CFirefighters urged to take part in
OL,4,Csurvey around mental health and work
OL,6,F"Firefighting is an intensive and
OL,7,Fhighly skilled profession, and every
OL,8,Fday we hear from firefighters who are
OL,9,Ffacing increasing and preventable
OL,10,Fpressures at work.
OL,12,F"Firefighters are being let down by
OL,13,Fpatchy and inconsistent support,
OL,14,Fwithout standard policies.
OL,16,F"We need firefighters across the UK to
OL,17,Ftake this survey and help build a
OL,18,Fclearer picture of how fire and rescue
OL,19,Fservices can better support the front
OL,20,Fline.
